CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 9, 1966, pg. 9B reads: "Graduation And birthday Party - Mrs. Henrietta Gaines gave a graduation party for her grandson DeWayne Ketchum. Theodore Ketchum was also celebrating his birthday.  The guests attending the party were: Marsha Broadie, Jean Cousar, Robert Cousar, Deborah Davis, Monte Dawson, Jr., Mark Ellison, Sandra Ely, Anthony Fountain, Evelie Jackson, Mary Kinsley, Gloria Larson, George Lee, Rhonda Lockette, Thelma Lovette, Wayne Peelre, Paulette Short, Antoinette Shorter, Ben Skelton and Sam Ware. (Harris Photo). (see title for corrected names).
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of young men and women, seated from left: Everly Jackson, Paulette Shorter, DeWayne Ketchum, Theodore Ketchum, Mary Kinsley, Theodore Ketchum, Rhonda Lockette; standing: Robert Cousar, Deborah Davis, Mark Ellison, Sam Ware, Sandra Eli, Anthony Fountain, Thelma Lovette, Jean Cousar, Marsha Brodie, Wayne Peeler, Gloria Larson, and Benny Skelton posed in backyard underneath maple tree for graduation party, Highland View Street, Penn Hills, another version
